description: Mama juice truck is a mobile destination using only the highest and freshest quality organic non-gmo, gluten-free local produce. Their mandate is that health and well-being should be within reach for everyone, so they are making it more accessible for the people of south Florida to live a better life. These are medicinal-strength juices that are always 100% organic, super food smoothies, and other tasty treats. Mama Juice is spreading the juice love to communities with delicious, nutritious, and healthy food options that truly bring a smile to all faces.
name: Mama Juice Truck
